Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.annotations

Annotation Interface SqlOnFhirConformance

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({METHOD,TYPE}) public @interface SqlOnFhirConformance
The SQL on FHIR conformance level. This allows us to map a feature within Pathling to a grouping of features within the specification.
